channel.title: Earthscape compiling Error
channel.description:

Go to the place where i posted this attachment and download the other one called .file_store_32 ...it will not work untill you have got that and placed it in a file called CACHE! THEN compile all the java files.

Compiling... The system cannot find the path specified. Compiling Completed! Press any key to continue
WHAT IS WRONG WHIT IT PLZ HELP :eek: (soz if i posted this in the wrong place...)
